{"timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:31:33.363830Z","level":"INFO","fields":{"message":"[BOT OUT] Chat: 1725327216 | Msg: 🤖 <b>Kaspa Platinum Command Center</b> | ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ | Welcome! This system provides secure, real-time Kaspa wallet monitoring directly via a private node. |  | 📌 <b>Public Commands:</b> | <code>/add &lt;address&gt;</code> - Track a wallet | <code>/remove &lt;address&gt;</code> - Stop tracking | <code>/list</code> - View your portfolio | <code>/balance</code> - Check live balances | <code>/network</code> - Network statistics | <code>/fees</code> - Live mempool fees | <code>/price</code> - Current KAS price | <code>/supply</code> - Circulating supply | <code>/market</code> - Market capitalization | <code>/dag</code> - BlockDAG details |  | 👑 <b>Admin Commands:</b> | <code>/sys</code> - Server Diagnostics | <code>/pause</code> - Disconnect Engine | <code>/resume</code> - Reconnect Engine | <code>/restart</code> - Reboot Process | <code>/broadcast &lt;msg&gt;</code> - Message all users | <code>/logs</code> - View System Logs"},"target":"kaspa_rust_bot::utils","span":{"action":"telegram_dispatch","chat_id":"ChatId(1725327216)","markup":"Some(KeyboardMarkup { keyboard: [[KeyboardButton { text: \"/balance\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/network\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/fees\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/supply\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/price\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/market\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/dag\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/list\", request: None }]], is_persistent: false, resize_keyboard: true, one_time_keyboard: false, input_field_placeholder: \"\", selective: false })","text":"🤖 <b>Kaspa Platinum Command Center</b>\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nWelcome! This system provides secure, real-time Kaspa wallet monitoring directly via a private node.\n\n📌 <b>Public Commands:</b>\n<code>/add &lt;address&gt;</code> - Track a wallet\n<code>/remove &lt;address&gt;</code> - Stop tracking\n<code>/list</code> - View your portfolio\n<code>/balance</code> - Check live balances\n<code>/network</code> - Network statistics\n<code>/fees</code> - Live mempool fees\n<code>/price</code> - Current KAS price\n<code>/supply</code> - Circulating supply\n<code>/market</code> - Market capitalization\n<code>/dag</code> - BlockDAG details\n\n👑 <b>Admin Commands:</b>\n<code>/sys</code> - Server Diagnostics\n<code>/pause</code> - Disconnect Engine\n<code>/resume</code> - Reconnect Engine\n<code>/restart</code> - Reboot Process\n<code>/broadcast &lt;msg&gt;</code> - Message all users\n<code>/logs</code> - View System Logs","name":"send_and_log"},"spans":[{"action":"telegram_dispatch","chat_id":"ChatId(1725327216)","markup":"Some(KeyboardMarkup { keyboard: [[KeyboardButton { text: \"/balance\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/network\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/fees\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/supply\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/price\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/market\", request: None }], [KeyboardButton { text: \"/dag\", request: None }, KeyboardButton { text: \"/list\", request: None }]], is_persistent: false, resize_keyboard: true, one_time_keyboard: false, input_field_placeholder: \"\", selective: false })","text":"🤖 <b>Kaspa Platinum Command Center</b>\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\nWelcome! This system provides secure, real-time Kaspa wallet monitoring directly via a private node.\n\n📌 <b>Public Commands:</b>\n<code>/add &lt;address&gt;</code> - Track a wallet\n<code>/remove &lt;address&gt;</code> - Stop tracking\n<code>/list</code> - View your portfolio\n<code>/balance</code> - Check live balances\n<code>/network</code> - Network statistics\n<code>/fees</code> - Live mempool fees\n<code>/price</code> - Current KAS price\n<code>/supply</code> - Circulating supply\n<code>/market</code> - Market capitalization\n<code>/dag</code> - BlockDAG details\n\n👑 <b>Admin Commands:</b>\n<code>/sys</code> - Server Diagnostics\n<code>/pause</code> - Disconnect Engine\n<code>/resume</code> - Reconnect Engine\n<code>/restart</code> - Reboot Process\n<code>/broadcast &lt;msg&gt;</code> - Message all users\n<code>/logs</code> - View System Logs","name":"send_and_log"}]}
